      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"interactiveDenoiser.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544641793/interactiveDenoiser.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763056158723&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=172\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544641793/interactiveDenoiser.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763056158723&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"222\" data-width=\"980\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"665485358\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"interactiveDenoiser.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544641793\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"2641a741-6a78-4cc6-ac59-8cf2a5f1e041\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544641793/interactiveDenoiser.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763056158723&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=980&amp;height=222 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544641793/interactiveDenoiser.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763056158723&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=172 1x\"></span><p>Please note that enabling the interactive denoiser on the RenderMan Render Settings LOP will automatically add the requested AOVs for denoising if those are not already present.</p><p><strong>Cheap First Pass</strong><br/>If checked, the first pass will use a cheaper (slightly faster but lower quality) heuristic.</p><p>This can be useful if rendering something that is converging very quickly and you want to prioritize getting a denoised result faster.</p><p><strong>Min Samples</strong><br/>The minimum number of average samples per bucket before the interactive denoiser runs for the first time.  Changing this preference requires the render to be restarted for this option to be respected</p><p><strong>Interval</strong><br/>The time interval in between denoise runs (in seconds)</p><p /><div class=\"panel conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"\" data-macro-name=\"panel\" style=\"background-color: #EAE6FF;border-color: #998DD9;border-width: 1px;\"><div class=\"panelContent\" style=\"background-color: #EAE6FF;\">\n<p>Note : To enhance interactivity when working on asset lookdev, try increasing the min samples to 8-10 and reduce back down to 2 - 4 when working on a larger scene.</p>\n</div></div><p />"
    }
  },
